{"tid":720554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女青年會主管被揭曾偷拍裙底","createTime":"2018-06-28T03:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T04:31:33.000Z","uid":44199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a27418e6c351f394c36470fbc35c5838bb73c2","tid":720554,"uid":44199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180627/large/27lp3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180627%2Flarge%2F27lp3p3.jpg&h=62eb5f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYWCA的陸耀盈日前接受Innovix盤問時，否認屬意BT勝出或同意由BT找其他公司入標以湊夠數。他接受代表Tech-21的大律師盤問時，承認有10項不誠實取用電腦罪的案底，今年1月被判感化令。他稱已向競委會透露有案底，亦有向YWCA總幹事匯報，沒受內部紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n陸昨再被問及案底細節，他稱去年7月在中環開會後，午膳時間在國際金融中心尾隨女途人，警察感可疑截查，從他手機撿取到一些偷拍裙底影片。他稱裙底片不是當日拍攝，最初因遊蕩被捕，後被控不誠實取用電腦罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180627/20432685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20432685&d=RVSoYN9NSAwllqBm4pv6Df%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=fd38a7af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20432685&h=79f4e757\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180627/20432685</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>正呀! 女青年會入邊咁多女青年, 呢條友一定可以日日瘋狂拍人裙底, 諗起都爽呀</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ce062a92c03a5203b64e65383e8a9b081802e8","tid":720554,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"049b5a7d06027aa98d4d2b1461ef02d60b408680","tid":